      "text": [
        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"مَنْ ذَهَبَ فِي حَاجَةٍ عَلَى غَيْرِ وُضُوءٍ فَلَمْ تُقْضَ حَاجَتُهُ فَلاَ يَلُومَنَّ إِلاَّ نَفْسَهُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3578 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"Whoever goes to fulfill a need without being in a state of ablution, and his need is not fulfilled, let him blame none but himself.\""
        ]
      }
    },
